<p>2016 is the Year of the Router (as crowned by John and Dave), and this week&#39;s episode includes some discussion about exactly how to choose the best router for your setup&#8230; especially if you&#39;re a geek. Bluetooth devices, too, are ubiquitous among us, and a few listeners are having trouble with theirs so John and Dave take to the mailbag to answer those questions, too. Plus, the entire episode begins with Cool Stuff Found. It&#39;s guaranteed to be entertaining&nbsp;<em>and</em>&nbsp;informative from beginning to end. That&#39;s infotainment, folks!</p>
